reviews.text: Braised (Lo bath) varieties of Teochew dishes including geese, duck, pork, egg, bean curl and offal are available in this shop. Cuttlefish is also served with bean curl and rice. Price is reasonable and food is good. That should be great if oyster omelet will also be available, but it is not found in the menu. Takeaway meal boxes with rice is the very good selection for quite bite.
鹵水味道一般，可以。買過牛筋，幾特別。但太硬，食吾倒。
鹵水好香，試過鴨，墨魚，鵝紅，豬耳，樣樣都唔錯，佢盒辣椒油都好味
